<br>
Cleri archetype skills are just TOO good. I want them all! Gimme gimme gimme!<br>
<br>
As of this post, I have 26 AAs now. I can't stop! That makes 8 I've gained now in 57th season. I plan on getting two more (I'm more than four yellow through one of those two) and then heading on to level 57.<br>
<br>
Why? I don't know. I can't help it. Plus I have been in a lot of groups the past few nights and the experience (well, the AAXP) seems to be flowing like..uh.. peridots on a raid.<br>
<br>
So.. I dinged 55, and spent 12 on Spellcasting Mastery III. Since then, I've spent 6 to get Healing Gift II and spent two to get Mental Clarity I. Right now I plan on getting a &quot;ME&quot; AA ability, Spellcasting Fury.<br>
<br>
Why &quot;ME&quot;?  Well.. because it will be fun for me to get crits and such, with spells and hammer.<br>
<br>
And &quot;ME&quot; too because ME is the place I like to hunt. Maiden's Eye. The crits will be fun there.<br>
<br>
So anyway, I plan on socking away 6 to 8 AA points each level now up until 60. I want to get Mental Clarity II and Healing Gift III in 57, then I'll probably branch out a bit in 58, getting a few like Healing Adept I, Channeling Focus I, and Spellcasting Reinforcement I. <br>
<br>
Anyway. I know I really shouldn't plan this far ahead, but I'm having a riot with these new abilities.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=destrea>Destrea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>The Kiss-It-Better Queen</span><br>  Posts: 85<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(8/18/03 2:01 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm45.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=89.topic&index=22>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.chivalrousvalor.com/sigs/ddoll.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: AA Craziness!</span><hr size=1> /hijack<br>
