<br>
Luclin<br>
Spell Casting Expertise<br>
This ability removes the chance that a player will fizzle when casting a spell.<br>
level 1. 1-20<br>
level 2. 1-35<br>
level 3. 1-52<br>
<br>
PoP<br>
Mastery of the Past<br>
This ability makes it impossible to fizzle spells.<br>
level 1. 1-54<br>
level 2. 1-56<br>
level 3. 1-58<br>
