<br>
Regen 3 will heal you 3 hitpoints every tic (6 seconds)... ie it takes 5 tics (30seconds) for it to heal 15 hit points.<br>
<br>
Basically I would definatly go regeneration before sta, it is not wildly difficult to max your sta with equipment and buffs, but maxing your regen is quite hard. And I personally would prefer an extra 3 hp's per tic to 15hp's total.<br>
<br>
